name: Syed Salma
bio: Hello! I am Salma, a Computer Science and Engineering graduate from KIYTS, with a keen interest in Artificial Intelligence (AI), Machine Learning (ML), and Python programming. Currently, I am working on enhancing my skills in AI technologies and Python, focusing on developing automation systems, data-driven applications, and AI models. I am always excited to explore new advancements in the field of Deep Learning, Computer Vision, and Natural Language Processing (NLP).
